  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a clinical study investigating pharmacokinetics, pharmacodynamic effects and safety
      of BAY 59-7939 in patients with atrial fibrillation (originally described in Japanese).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
